{'text': 'When do we decriminalize prostitution? When do we legalize gambling? When do we decriminalize alcohol and tobacco?'}
{'text': "#5. \xa0If we legalize drugs, then a lot of good people will end up getting arrested for possession of a drug that isn't even illegal in the first place."}
{'text': "#4. \xa0 If we legalize drugs, then we'll lose the negative effects of prohibition without actually gaining any of the positive effects of legalization."}
{'text': 'It would be better to legalize drugs rather than trying to eradicate them.'}
{'text': 'No one is talking about legalizing the sale of alcohol, tobacco, or other recreational products. Why are we downplaying the dangers of illegal drug use?'}
{'text': 'If we legalize drugs, we will end up with people who are unwilling to do drugs, but not willing to pay for them.'}
{'text': '#4. \xa0Drugs are a bad thing. \xa0It would be good for society if we could prevent the use of drugs.'}
{'text': '#7. \xa0If drugs are legalized, can we control them? Of course!'}
{'text': "#1. Legalizing drugs will probably lead to more crime. Drug dealers will have more power, and more people will be addicted to their products. It's going to be a nightmare for society."}
{'text': "#4. \xa0We shouldn't legalize drugs. We should legalize sex instead. It's more socially acceptable. It's more pleasant. And it doesn't make people addicted to drugs."}
{'text': 'Now that drugs are legal, there will be less drug addiction, and maybe even less drug abuse. This is an important step in reducing the damage caused by the drug war.'}
{'text': 'This is not the right time to worry about drugs.'}
{'text': '#5. \xa0There will be a huge increase in the illegal drug market if we legalize drugs. \xa0If we legalize drugs, the government will be forced to enforce the drug laws.'}
{'text': "It's important to understand the difference between legalizing drugs, and decriminalizing drugs. Decriminalizing means making it a crime to possess drugs, but not to sell them."}
{'text': '#17. Not all drugs are created equal.'}
